    "description": "这个故事发生在热带的某个地方。 在天空中，靠近一个大泻湖的地方出现了发光的灯光，即使在水下也能看到它们。 然后一些物体开始从天上掉下来......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/405c94fe74847dfa3190cf3b6df85fa7.poster.avif?t=1742541148\" width=618 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/405c94fe74847dfa3190cf3b6df85fa7.webm?t=1742541148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/405c94fe74847dfa3190cf3b6df85fa7.mp4?t=1742541148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一款适合全家人的大气水下游戏，具有精美的图形、令人难忘的音乐、成就和故事情节。<br>在这个游戏中，你必须控制一条灵活的鱼。 躲避奇怪的坠落物体，留意饥饿程度并在海底寻找珠宝！<br>您将参观各种水下地点并与最终老板面对面……但也许他不是恶棍……？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/95591070d607dbb289520143cdaec0e9.poster.avif?t=1742541148\" width=618 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/95591070d607dbb289520143cdaec0e9.webm?t=1742541148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800980/extras/95591070d607dbb289520143cdaec0e9.mp4?t=1742541148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>帮助勇敢的鱼解开灯光之谜！",
